@nourishatelier_travels : For the swedes ♡ my Singapore Guide is out in the latest issue of @restravelmagazine with the best places to eat, sleep and and wander around. Singapore is THE food destination and even offers the cheapest michelin starred meal in the world 🍽. The whole city is like a kaleidoscope of flavours and visuals. Half of the time I was there I felt like I was walking in a film set from a pastel coloured musical. A truly fascinating place. And now that @SingaporeAir 🛩 flies direct to Singapore from Stockholm it's just a step, som blockbusters and a nap away from you. Get the full guide at the newsstands 
#singapore #beautifuldestinations

